{
  "character_description": "The Rubber Chicken is a classic yellow rubber chicken toy come to life, with a bumpy yellow body, long neck, red comb and wattle, orange beak, orange feet, silly blue eyes, and a green collar. It fights through squeaks, floppy wings, stretched rubber limbs, and absurd elastic recoil.\n\nSilhouette: tall skinny rubber chicken with long neck, tiny wings, and orange feet.\nClothing: none, toy body only.\nHair: red rubber comb.\nAccessories: green collar band.\nAttitude: frantic, squeaky, ridiculous, surprisingly dangerous.\nDistinctive traits: elastic neck snaps, rubber wobble, squeak-ring projectile effects.",
